<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1 class="display-4">About Us</h1>
            <p class="lead">Welcome to our burger place! We are committed to providing the best burgers in town. Our ingredients are fresh, our recipes are delicious, and our service is top-notch. Our journey began with a passion for creating mouthwatering burgers that leave our customers craving for more.</p>
            <p>We believe that every bite should be a delightful experience. That's why we carefully select our ingredients to ensure the highest quality and flavor in every burger. From juicy beef patties to crispy vegetables, we take pride in delivering an exceptional taste that satisfies all cravings.</p>
            <p>Our team of dedicated chefs and staff work tirelessly to bring you the perfect blend of flavors and textures. Whether you're a meat lover, a vegetarian, or looking for a vegan option, our diverse menu has something for everyone.</p>
            <p>So come join us at our cozy and welcoming restaurant. Indulge in the ultimate burger experience that's crafted with love, creativity, and a dedication to making every visit unforgettable.</p>
            <p>We look forward to serving you and making your burger cravings a reality!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and jQuery (for dropdowns, modals, etc.) -->
